/// Circuit Diagram (Text-based)

ESP32 DevKit

                +---------------------------+
   Potentiometer | GPIO34 (ADC)             |
                 |                          |
   Button ------>| GPIO25 (INPUT_PULLUP)    |
                 |                          |
   LED Green --->| GPIO26 (OUTPUT)          |
   LED Yellow -->| GPIO27 (OUTPUT)          |
   LED Red   --->| GPIO14 (OUTPUT)          |
                 |                          |
   HC-SR04 #1    | TRIG = GPIO32            |
                 | ECHO = GPIO33            |
                 |                          |
   HC-SR04 #2    | TRIG = GPIO4             |
                 | ECHO = GPIO5             |
                +---------------------------+

- Potentiometer (10kΩ):  
   - VCC → 3.3V  
   - GND → GND  
   - Middle pin → GPIO34  

- Button (Pull-up config):  
   - One side → GPIO25  
   - Other side → GND  

- LEDs (with 220Ω resistors each):  
   - Anode (+) → GPIO26 / 27 / 14  
   - Cathode (-) → GND  

- HC-SR04 sensors:  
   - VCC → 5V  
   - GND → GND  
   - TRIG/ECHO → as assigned above
